<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Rebel Wilson has been on a health and fitness journey so far this year, losing at least 18kg (40lbs or 2.8 stone).</p>

<p>And on Thursday, the Australian actress took a day off from training to enjoy a pampering session in Los Angeles.</p>

<p>The 40-year-old comedian showed off her slimmed-down frame while visiting a skincare spa.</p>

<p>Relaxing stroll: Rebel Wilson, who is in the midst of a weight loss journey, took a day off from training on Thursday to enjoy a pampering session in Los Angeles</p>

<p>The Isn't It Romantic star looked stylish in a striped T-shirt and black leggings, which she paired with flat shoes and a handbag.</p>

<p>She concealed her gaze behind cat-eye sunglasses, styled her hair in a ponytail with a scrunchie, and also wore a face mask.</p>

<p>Last month, Rebel updated fans on her weight loss journey by sharing several photos to Instagram of herself looking slimmer in a tight blue dress. </p>

<p>Looking good! The 40-year-old showed off her slimmer frame while visiting a skincare spa</p>

<p>Casual chic: The Isn't It Romantic star looked stylish in a striped T-shirt and black leggings, which she paired with flat shoes and a handbag</p>

<p>The Bridesmaids star explained in the caption that she was inching closer and closer to her goal weight of 75kg (165lbs, or 11.8 stone).</p>

<p>'Thanks for all the love so far on my "Year of Health" journey,' she told her followers.</p>

<p>'When I was reaching for the candies last night after dinner I thought to myself 'hmmmm...better not' and had a bottle of water instead.'</p>

<p>'Eight kilos to go until I hit my goal. Hopefully I can do it by the end of the year.'</p>

<p>Wow! Last month, Rebel updated fans on her weight loss journey by sharing photos to Instagram of herself looking slimmer in a tight blue dress (left). Right: Rebel in May 2019</p>

<p>Rebel announced in January that she was going to make her health a priority in 2020.</p>

<p>'So for me 2020 is going to be called the "Year of Health". So I put on the athleisure and went out for a walk, deliberately hydrating on the couch right now,' she said.</p>

<p>'And [I'm] trying to avoid the sugar and junk food, which is going to be hard after the holidays I've just had but I'm going to do it!' </p>

<p>'Year of health': Rebel announced in January that she was going to make her health a priority in 2020. Pictured on August 16</p>

<p>Kilo by kilo: Rebel revealed in May that she was trying to get down to her goal weight of 75kg (165lbs or 11.8 stone)</p>
